<eesti>&sect; 1. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 1. </inglise>
<eesti>Maksu objekt </eesti>
<inglise>Object of taxation </inglise>
<eesti>K&auml;ibemaksuga maksustatakse k&auml;esoleva seaduse paragrahvis 4 s&auml;testatud maksustatav k&auml;ive. </eesti>
<inglise>Value added tax is imposed on taxable supply provided for in &sect; 4 of this Act. </inglise>
<eesti>K&auml;ibemaksu rakendatakse lisandunud v&auml;&auml;rtuse maksuna. </eesti>
<inglise>Value added tax is applied as tax on added value. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 2. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 2. </inglise>
<eesti>M&otilde;isted </eesti>
<inglise>Definitions </inglise>
<eesti>K&auml;esolevas seaduses kasutatakse m&otilde;isteid j&auml;rgmises t&auml;henduses: </eesti>
<inglise>In this Act, the following definitions are used: </inglise>
<eesti>1) ettev&otilde;tlus - isiku iseseisev majandustegevus, mille k&auml;igus toimub kauba v&otilde;i teenuse tasuline v&otilde;i tasuta v&otilde;&otilde;randamine. </eesti>
<inglise>1) "enterprise" means the independent economic activity of a person in the course of which goods or services are transferred for a charge or without charge. </inglise>
<eesti>Ettev&otilde;tlusena k&auml;sitatakse ka notari ja kohtut&auml;ituri ametitegevust. </eesti>
<inglise>A notary's and a bailiff's professional activities are also deemed to be enterprise. </inglise>
<eesti>T&ouml;&ouml;tamine t&ouml;&ouml;lepingu alusel ja avalik teenistus ning mittetulundus&uuml;hingute ja sihtasutuste p&otilde;hikirjaliste eesm&auml;rkide saavutamisele suunatud tegevus ei ole ettev&otilde;tlus; </eesti>
<inglise>Employment under an employment contract, public service and activities aimed at achieving the objectives specified in the articles of association of a non-profit association or foundation are deemed not to be enterprise; </inglise>
<eesti>(17.11.1999 j&otilde;ust.01.01.2000 - RT I 1999, 92, 823; 17.01.2001 j&otilde;ust.01.03.2001 - RT I 2001, 16, 69) </eesti>
<inglise>(17.11.1999 entered into force 01.01.2000 - RT I 1999, 92, 823; 17.01.2001 entered into force 01.03.2001 - RT I 2001, 16, 69) </inglise>
<eesti>2) kaubad - vallasasjad, loomad, puisteained, vedelikud, gaasid, elektri- ja soojusenergia. </eesti>
<inglise>2) "goods" means movables, animals, bulk substances, liquids, gases, electric power and heat. </inglise>
<eesti>Kinnisasjad ja laevakinnistusraamatusse kantud laevad, ehitised kui vallasasjad, raha ja v&auml;&auml;rtpaberid ei ole kaubad; </eesti>
<inglise>Immovables and ships entered in the ship register, structures as movables, money and securities are deemed not to be goods; </inglise>
<eesti>(11.02.98 j&otilde;ust.01.07.98 - RT I 1998, 23, 321; 17.11.1999 j&otilde;ust.01.01.2000 - RT I 1999, 92, 823) </eesti>
<inglise>(11.02.98 entered into force 01.07.98 - RT I 1998, 23, 321; 17.11.1999 entered into force 01.01.2000 - RT I 1999, 92, 823) </inglise>
<eesti>3) teenused - k&otilde;ik k&auml;esoleva paragrahvi punktis 2 h&otilde;lmamata, ettev&otilde;tluse korras osutatavad h&uuml;ved, sealhulgas v&otilde;&otilde;randatavad &otilde;igused </eesti>
<inglise>3) "services" means all benefits provided through enterprise which are not included in clause 2) of this section, including transferable rights; </inglise>
<eesti>(17.11.1999 j&otilde;ust.01.01.2000 - RT I 1999, 92, 823) </eesti>
<inglise>(17.11.1999 entered into force 01.01.2000 - RT I 1999, 92, 823) </inglise>
<eesti>4) m&uuml;&uuml;ja - isik, kes v&otilde;&otilde;randab kaupu v&otilde;i teenuseid; </eesti>
<inglise>4) "seller" means a person who transfers goods or services; </inglise>
<eesti>5) isik - f&uuml;&uuml;siline ja juriidiline isik, riigi-, valla- ja linnaasutus tema majandustegevuse osas, v&auml;lismaa &auml;ri&uuml;hingu filiaal ning Eestis maksukorralduse seaduses (RT I 1994, 1, 5; 2000, 45, 279; 55, 365, 84, 533, 534) s&auml;testatud p&uuml;sivat tegevuskohta omav v&auml;lismaa juriidiline isik; </eesti>
<inglise>5) "person" means a natural or legal person, a state, rural municipality or city agency with regard to its economic activities, a branch of a foreign company, or a foreign legal person who has a permanent establishment in Estonia provided for in the Taxation Act (RT I 1994, 1, 5; 2000, 45, 279, 55, 365; 84, 533, 534); </inglise>
<eesti>(17.11.1999 j&otilde;ust.01.01.2000 - RT I 1999, 92, 823) </eesti>
<inglise>(17.11.1999 entered into force 01.01.2000 - RT I 1999, 92, 823) </inglise>
<eesti>6) import - kauba sissevedu Eesti tolliterritooriumile tolliprotseduuriga "import vabaks ringluseks", samuti renditud kauba ajutine sissevedu taasv&auml;ljaveo kohustusega ning t&ouml;&ouml;tlemiseks v&auml;ljaviidud kauba taassissevedu tolliseaduse (RT I 1993, 62, 891; 76, 1129; 1994, 30, 466; 1995, 20, 297) m&otilde;istes; </eesti>
<inglise>6) "import" means the importation of goods into the Estonian customs territory under the customs procedure "import for free circulation", the temporary importation of leased goods subject to re-exportation and the re-importation of goods exported for outward processing, as defined in the Customs Act (RT I 1993, 62, 891; 76, 1129; 1994, 30, 466; 1995, 20, 297); </inglise>
<eesti>7) eksport - kauba v&auml;ljavedu Eesti tolliterritooriumilt v&otilde;i kauba toimetamine vabatsooni tolliprotseduuriga "eksport", t&ouml;&ouml;tlemiseks Eestisse sissetoodud kaubale Eestis lisatud materjalide v&auml;ljavedu tolliprotseduuriga "taasv&auml;ljavedu" ning teenuse eksport k&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect; 13 4. l&otilde;ikes s&auml;testatud t&auml;henduses; </eesti>
<inglise>7) "export" means the exportation of goods from the Estonian customs territory or the conveyance of goods into a free zone under the customs procedure "exportation", the exportation, under the customs procedure "re-exportation", of materials added in Estonia to goods imported into Estonia for outward processing, and the export of services as defined in subsection 13 (4) of this Act. </inglise>
<eesti>(17.11.1999 j&otilde;ust.01.01.2000 - RT I 1999, 92, 823) </eesti>
<inglise>(17.11.1999 entered into force 01.01.2000 - RT I 1999, 92, 823) </inglise>
<eesti>8) raamatud - v&auml;hemalt kolmest &uuml;ksteisega &uuml;hest servast &uuml;hendatud lehest koosnevad tr&uuml;kised, v&auml;lja arvatud perioodikav&auml;ljaanded, blanketiraamatud ning m&auml;rkmikud (sealhulgas kalenderm&auml;rkmikud ja &otilde;pilasp&auml;evikud. </eesti>
<inglise>8) "books" means printed matter consisting of at least three pages connected to each other at one edge, except for periodicals, books of pre-printed forms and notebooks (including diaries and students' study journals). </inglise>
<eesti>Raamatutena k&auml;sitatakse k&auml;esoleva seaduse m&otilde;istes ka tr&uuml;kitud geograafilisi, h&uuml;drograafilisi jms kaarte. </eesti>
<inglise>For the purposes of this Act, printed geographical, hydrographic and other such maps are also deemed to be books. </inglise>
<eesti>(23.09.98 j&otilde;ust.01.01.99 - RT I 1998, 86/87, 1410; 17.11.1999 j&otilde;ust.01.01.2000 - RT I 1999, 92, 823) </eesti>
<inglise>(23.09.98 entered into force 01.01.99 - RT I 1998, 86/87, 1410; 17.11.1999 entered into force 01.01.2000 - RT I 1999, 92, 823) </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 3. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 3. </inglise>
<eesti>K&auml;ive </eesti>
<inglise>Supply </inglise>
<eesti>(1) K&auml;esoleva seaduse t&auml;henduses loetakse k&auml;ibeks: </eesti>
<inglise>(1) For the purposes of this Act, the following are deemed to be supply: </inglise>
<eesti>1) kaupade ja teenuste m&uuml;&uuml;ki, vahetamist ning tasuta v&otilde;&otilde;randamist; </eesti>
<inglise>1) the sale, exchange or transfer without charge of goods or services; </inglise>
<eesti>2) kaupade v&otilde;i teenuste tarbimist maksukohustuslase enda poolt k&auml;esoleva paragrahvi 2. l&otilde;ikes s&auml;testatud juhtudel. </eesti>
<inglise>2) the consumption of goods or services by a taxable person in the cases provided for in subsection (2) of this section. </inglise>
<eesti>(17.11.1999 j&otilde;ust.01.01.2000 - RT I 1999, 92, 823) </eesti>
<inglise>(17.11.1999 entered into force 01.01.2000 - RT I 1999, 92, 823) </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Kaupade ja teenuste tarbimine maksukohustuslase enda poolt loetakse k&auml;ibeks j&auml;rgmistel juhtudel: </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The consumption of goods or services by a taxable person is deemed to be supply in the following cases: </inglise>
<eesti>1) kaupade andmine ja teenuste osutamine t&ouml;&ouml;andja poolt t&ouml;&ouml;v&otilde;tjale t&ouml;&ouml;tasu, preemia v&otilde;i muu v&auml;ljamakse katteks, kui registreeritud maksukohustuslane on nende kaupade ja teenuste soetamisel makstud k&auml;ibemaksu enda k&auml;ibelt arvestatud k&auml;ibemaksust maha arvanud; </eesti>
<inglise>1) the provision of goods or services by an employer to an employee in lieu of remuneration, a bonus or other payment if such registered taxable person has deducted the value added tax paid upon the purchase of such goods or services from the value added tax calculated on its own supply; </inglise>
<eesti>2) (Kehtetu - 07.11.96 j&otilde;ust.08.12.96 - RT I 1996, 81, 1447) </eesti>
<inglise>2) (Repealed - 07.11.96 entered into force 08.12.96 - RT I 1996, 81, 1447) </inglise>
<eesti>3) enda toodetud kaupade v&otilde;&otilde;randamine ja teenuste osutamine loteriiv&otilde;itudeks loterii korraldaja poolt. </eesti>
<inglise>3) the transfer by an organiser of a lottery of goods produced by the organiser of the lottery, or the provision by an organiser of a lottery of services as a lottery prize. </inglise>
<eesti>(12.06.96 j&otilde;ust.01.09.96 - RT I 1996, 44, 845) </eesti>
<inglise>(12.06.96 entered into force 01.09.96 - RT I 1996, 44, 845) </inglise>
<eesti>(3) K&auml;esolevas seaduses k&auml;sitatakse kasutusrenti teenuse v&otilde;&otilde;randamisena ja kaupade kapitalirenti kaupade v&otilde;&otilde;randamisena. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) For the purposes of this Act, operating lease is deemed to be transfer of services and financial lease of goods is deemed to be the transfer of the goods. </inglise>
<eesti>Kapitalirendilepingus peab olema s&auml;testatud omandi&otilde;iguse &uuml;leminek kauba v&auml;ljaostmisel, vastasel korral loetakse tehing kasutusrendiks. </eesti>
<inglise>The transfer of the right of ownership upon the purchase of goods shall be provided for in the financial lease contract; otherwise the transaction is deemed to be an operating lease. </inglise>
<eesti>(17.11.1999 j&otilde;ust.01.01.2000 - RT I 1999, 92, 823) </eesti>
<inglise>(17.11.1999 entered into force 01.01.2000 - RT I 1999, 92, 823) </inglise>
<eesti>(4) K&auml;esoleva seaduse t&auml;henduses ei loeta k&auml;ibeks: </eesti>
<inglise>(4) For the purposes of this Act, the following are deemed not to be supply: </inglise>
<eesti>1) mitterahalisi sissemakseid &auml;ri&uuml;hingu osa- v&otilde;i aktsiakapitali; </eesti>
<inglise>1) a non-monetary contribution to the share capital of a company; </inglise>
<eesti>2) kaupade omandi&otilde;iguse &uuml;leminekut tollilaos v&otilde;i vabatsoonis; </eesti>
<inglise>2) the transfer of the right of ownership of goods in a customs warehouse or free zone; </inglise>
<eesti>(17.11.1999 j&otilde;ust.01.01.2000 - RT I 1999, 92, 823) </eesti>
<inglise>(17.11.1999 entered into force 01.01.2000 - RT I 1999, 92, 823) </inglise>
<eesti>3) erastamisnimekirja kantud riigi-, valla- v&otilde;i linnavara erastamist, riigivara valla v&otilde;i linna omandisse andmist, kaupade andmist ja teenuste osutamist osakute eest p&otilde;llumajandusreformi k&auml;igus ning kinnistusraamatusse kandmata mitmeaastaste istanduste &uuml;leandmist &otilde;igustatud subjektidele maareformi k&auml;igus; </eesti>
<inglise>3) the privatisation of state, rural municipality or city assets entered in the privatisation list, the transfer of state assets into the ownership of a rural municipality or city, the provision of goods or services for units in the course of agricultural reform, or the transfer of plantations of permanent crops which are not entered in the land register to entitled subjects in the course of land reform; </inglise>
<eesti>(17.11.1999 j&otilde;ust.01.01.2000 - RT I 1999, 92, 823) </eesti>
<inglise>(17.11.1999 entered into force 01.01.2000 - RT I 1999, 92, 823) </inglise>
<eesti>4) vara &uuml;leandmist uutele ettev&otilde;tjatele &auml;riregistrisse kandmata ettev&otilde;tete &uuml;mberkujundamisel &auml;riseadustikus (RT I 1995, 26-28, 355; 1998, 91/93; 1999, 10, 155; 23, 355, 24, 360; 57, 596; 102, 907; 2000, 29, 172; 49, 303; 55, 365; 57, 373) s&auml;testatud ettev&otilde;tjateks; </eesti>
<inglise>4) the transfer of assets to a new undertaking upon the transformation of an enterprise which is not entered in the commercial register into an undertaking provided for in the Commercial Code (RT I 1995, 26-28, 355; 1998, 91/93; 1999, 10, 155; 23, 355, 24, 360; 57, 596; 102, 907; 2000, 29, 172; 49, 303; 55, 365; 57, 373) </inglise>
<eesti>5) debitoorse v&otilde;lgnevuse m&uuml;&uuml;ki (faktooring); </eesti>
<inglise>5) sale of accounts receivable (factoring); </inglise>
<eesti>6) kirjalikus lepingus etten&auml;htud viiviste ja leppetrahvide, samuti tekitatud kahju sissen&otilde;udmist; </eesti>
<inglise>6) the collection of a fine for delay or penalty prescribed in a written contract, and the collection of damages; </inglise>
<eesti>(17.11.1999 j&otilde;ust.01.01.2000 - RT I 1999, 92, 823) </eesti>
<inglise>(17.11.1999 entered into force 01.01.2000 - RT I 1999, 92, 823) </inglise>
<eesti>7) vara &uuml;leandmist teisele isikule &auml;ri&uuml;hingu &uuml;hinemisel, jagunemisel ja &uuml;mberkujundamisel &auml;riseadustiku m&otilde;istes; </eesti>
<inglise>7) the transfer of assets to other persons upon the merger, division or transformation of a company, as defined in the Commercial Code; </inglise>
<eesti>8) kauba, kinnisasja ja ehitise kui vallasasja vahetamise v&otilde;i parandamise teenuse osutamist garantiit&auml;htaja jooksul kauba, kinnisasja ja ehitise kui vallasasja valdajale; </eesti>
<inglise>8) the exchange or repair of goods, immovables or structures as movables to the holders of the goods or the possessors of the immovables or structures as movables, during the warranty period; </inglise>
<eesti>(07.11.96 j&otilde;ust.08.12.96 - RT I 1996, 81, 1447) </eesti>
<inglise>(07.11.96 entered into force 08.12.96 - RT I 1996, 81, 1447) </inglise>
<eesti>9) &uuml;he maksukohustuslasena registreeritud isikute omavahelisi tehinguid, kui tehingu tulemusena kauba v&otilde;i teenuse soetanud isik kasutab selle kauba v&otilde;i teenuse t&auml;ies ulatuses oma maksustatava k&auml;ibe tarbeks; </eesti>
<inglise>9) transactions between persons registered as a single taxable person, if, as a result of the transaction, the person who purchased goods or a service uses the goods or service in full for the purposes of the person's taxable supply; </inglise>
<eesti>(17.11.1999 j&otilde;ust.01.01.2000 - RT I 1999, 92, 823) </eesti>
<inglise>(17.11.1999 entered into force 01.01.2000 - RT I 1999, 92, 823) </inglise>
<eesti>10) Eesti Vabariigi seaduse "Eesti Kaubandus-T&ouml;&ouml;stuskoja Arbitraa&zcaron;ikohtu kohta" (RT 1991, 25, 308; 1999, 18, 302) t&auml;henduses vaidlevate poolte ja muudes vahekohtutes vaidlevate poolte poolt arbitraa&zcaron;imaksu tasumist. </eesti>
<inglise>10) payment of an arbitration fee by the parties to a dispute as defined in the Republic of Estonia Act on the Arbitral Tribunal of the Estonian Chamber of Commerce and Industry (RT 1991, 25, 308; 1999, 18, 302) or by the parties to a dispute before another arbitral tribunal. </inglise>
<eesti>(10.02.99 j&otilde;ust.05.03.99 - RT I 1999, 18, 302) </eesti>
<inglise>(10.02.99 entered into force 05.03.99 - RT I 1999, 18, 302) </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 4. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 4. </inglise>
<eesti>Maksustatav k&auml;ive </eesti>
<inglise>Taxable supply </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Maksustatav k&auml;ive k&auml;esoleva seaduse t&auml;henduses on Eestis toodetud v&otilde;i Eestisse imporditud vabas ringluses olevate kaupade ja Eestis osutatud teenuste k&auml;ive ning kaupade import, v&auml;lja arvatud k&auml;esoleva seaduse paragrahvis 5 s&auml;testatud maksuvaba k&auml;ive. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) For the purposes of this Act, taxable supply is the supply of goods which are produced in Estonia or imported into Estonia and are in free circulation, the supply of services provided in Estonia and the import of goods, except for supply exempt from tax provided for in &sect; 5 of this Act. </inglise>
<eesti>(12.06.96 j&otilde;ust.01.09.96 - RT I 1996, 44, 845) </eesti>
<inglise>(12.06.96 entered into force 01.09.96 - RT I 1996, 44, 845) </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Maksustatavalt k&auml;ibelt maksavad k&auml;ibemaksu maksukohustuslased k&auml;esolevas seaduses s&auml;testatud korras. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) Taxable persons shall pay value added tax on taxable supply pursuant to the procedure provided for in this Act. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Impordilt maksavad k&auml;ibemaksu maksukohustuslased ja k&otilde;ik teised Eestisse kaupu importivad isikud tollieeskirjadega (tolliseaduse m&otilde;istes) impordimaksude tasumiseks s&auml;testatud korras. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) Taxable persons and all other persons importing goods into Estonia shall pay value added tax on imports pursuant to the procedure for payment of import charges provided by the customs rules (as defined in the Customs Act). </inglise>
<eesti>(12.06.96 j&otilde;ust.01.09.96 - RT I 1996, 44, 845) </eesti>
<inglise>(12.06.96 entered into force 01.09.96 - RT I 1996, 44, 845) </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 5. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 5. </inglise>
<eesti>Maksuvaba k&auml;ive </eesti>
<inglise>Supply exempt from tax </inglise>
<eesti>(1) K&auml;ibemaksuga ei maksustata j&auml;rgmiste teenuste ja kaupade k&auml;ivet ning kaupade importi: </eesti>
<inglise>(1) Value added tax shall not be imposed on the supply of the following goods and services or on the import of the following goods: </inglise>
<eesti>1) alusharidus-, p&otilde;hiharidus-, keskharidus- ja k&otilde;rgharidus- ning t&auml;iendus- ja vabahariduskoolitus; </eesti>
<inglise>1) pre-school education, basic education, secondary education, higher education, in-service training and informal education; </inglise>
<eesti>2) postimaksevahendid ja riikliku postiside teenused; </eesti>
<inglise>2) postal payment means and state postal services; </inglise>
<eesti>3) Eesti Vabariigi ravikindlustusseaduse (RT 1991, 23, 272; 1992, 19, 276; RT I 1994, 23, 387; 1997, 28, 425; 1998, 111, 1829; 1999, 29, 397; 2000, 57, 374; 84, 536; 102, 675) kohaselt kinnitatud ravikindlustuse terviseuuringute ja raviteenuste hinnakirjas ning tasuliste meditsiiniteenuste hinnakirjas loetletud meditsiiniteenused; </eesti>
