<eesti>II peat&uuml;kk </eesti>
<inglise>Chapter II </inglise>
<eesti>Maksukohustuslaste registreerimine ja nende kohustused </eesti>
<inglise>Registration and Duties of Taxable Persons </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 6. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 6. </inglise>
<eesti>Maksukohustuslane </eesti>
<inglise>Taxable person </inglise>
<eesti>Maksukohustuslane on isik, kellel ettev&otilde;tluse tulemusel tekib maksustatav k&auml;ive. </eesti>
<inglise>A taxable person is a person who makes a taxable supply as a result of engagement in enterprise. </inglise>
<eesti>Riigi-, valla- v&otilde;i linnaasutust k&auml;sitatakse maksukohustuslasena sellise k&auml;ibe osas, millega ta konkureerib turul teiste maksukohustuslastega. </eesti>
<inglise>State, local government and city agencies are deemed to be taxable persons with regard to supply with which they compete on the market with other taxable persons. </inglise>
<eesti>(12.06.96 j&otilde;ust.01.09.96 - RT I 1996, 44, 845; 17.11.1999 j&otilde;ust.01.01.2000 - RT I 1999, 92, 823) </eesti>
<inglise>(12.06.96 entered into force 01.09.96 - RT I 1996, 44, 845; 17.11.1999 entered into force 01.01.2000 - RT I 1999, 92, 823) </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 7. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 7. </inglise>
<eesti>Maksukohustuslase registreerimine </eesti>
<inglise>Registration of taxable person </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Maksukohustuslane, kelle maksustatav k&auml;ive, v&auml;lja arvatud import, &uuml;letab kalendriaasta algusest arvates 250 000 krooni, on kohustatud 10 kalendrip&auml;eva jooksul, arvates nimetatud suuruses maksustatava k&auml;ibe tekkimise p&auml;evast, esitama oma elu- v&otilde;i asukohaj&auml;rgsele Maksuameti kohalikule asutusele (edaspidi Maksuamet) rahandusministri kehtestatud vormis avalduse enda registreerimiseks k&auml;ibemaksukohustuslasena (edaspidi registreerimine). </eesti>
<inglise>(1) A taxable person whose taxable supply, excluding imports, exceeds 250 000 kroons as calculated from the beginning of a calendar year is required to submit an application in the format established by the Minister of Finance for registration of the taxable person as a person liable to value added tax (hereinafter registration) to the local Tax Board office (hereinafter the Tax Board) of the residence or seat of the taxable person within ten calendar days after the date on which taxable supply reached the specified amount. </inglise>
<eesti>&Auml;riregistrisse kandmata juriidilisest isikust maksukohustuslane lisab avaldusele oma p&otilde;hikirja ja ettev&otilde;tteregistri poolt v&auml;ljaantud registreerimistunnistuse, &auml;riregistrisse kantud maksukohustuslane &auml;riregistri poolt v&auml;ljaantud registrikaardi &auml;rakirja. </eesti>
<inglise>A taxable person who is a legal person and is not entered in the commercial register shall annex the taxable person's articles of association and a copy of the registration certificate issued by the enterprise register to the application; a taxable person who is entered in the commercial register shall annex a copy of the registry card issued by the commercial register to the application. </inglise>
<eesti>Maksuamet registreerib maksukohustuslase k&auml;esolevas l&otilde;ikes nimetatud maksustatava k&auml;ibe tekkimise kuule j&auml;rgneva kalendrikuu esimesest p&auml;evast. </eesti>
<inglise>The Tax Board shall register the taxable person as of the first day of the calendar month following the month in which the taxable supply reached the amount specified in this subsection. </inglise>
<eesti>Maksukohustuslase, kes esitab avalduse k&auml;esolevas l&otilde;ikes etten&auml;htud t&auml;htaja jooksul, kuid k&auml;esolevas l&otilde;ikes nimetatud suuruses maksustatava k&auml;ibe tekkimise p&auml;evale j&auml;rgneval kalendrikuul, registreerib Maksuamet avalduse esitamise kuu esimesest p&auml;evast. </eesti>
<inglise>A taxable person who submits an application during the term prescribed in this section but during the calendar month following the date on which taxable supply reached the amount specified in this subsection shall be registered by the Tax Board as of the first day of the month in which the application is submitted. </inglise>
<eesti>(12.06.96 j&otilde;ust.01.09.96 - RT I 1996, 44, 845; 17.11.1999 j&otilde;ust.01.01.2000 - RT I 1999, 92, 823) </eesti>
<inglise>(12.06.96 entered into force 01.09.96 - RT I 1996, 44, 845; 17.11.1999 entered into force 01.01.2000 - RT I 1999, 92, 823) </inglise>
<eesti>(1 (1)) Registreerimiseks avalduse esitamisel peab f&uuml;&uuml;siline isik v&otilde;i juriidilise isiku esindaja esitama Maksuametile ka oma isikut t&otilde;endava dokumendi. </eesti>
<inglise>(1 (1)) Upon filing of an application for registration, a natural person or the representative of a legal person shall also submit his or her identity document to the Tax Board. </inglise>
<eesti>Kui avalduse esitamisel isikut t&otilde;endavat dokumenti ei esitata, on Maksuametil &otilde;igus avaldus isikule tagastada ja registreerida isik p&auml;rast isikut t&otilde;endava dokumendi esitamist. </eesti>
<inglise>If an identity document is not submitted upon submission of an application, the Tax Board has the right to return the application to the person and register the person after the identity document has been submitted. </inglise>
<eesti>Samuti on Maksuametil &otilde;igus avaldus isikule tagastada, kui avalduses esitatud andmed ei ole &otilde;iged v&otilde;i kui pole esitatud k&otilde;iki andmeid. </eesti>
<inglise>The Tax Board has the right to return an application to a person also if the information submitted in the application is incorrect or insufficient. </inglise>
<eesti>Maksuamet registreerib sellise isiku, kui ta esitab parandatud v&otilde;i t&auml;iendatud andmetega avalduse 10 kalendrip&auml;eva jooksul Maksuameti poolt tagastatud avalduse k&auml;ttesaamise p&auml;evast arvates. </eesti>
<inglise>The Tax Board shall register such person if the person files the application with corrected or supplemented information within ten calendar days after the date of receipt of the application returned by the Tax Board. </inglise>
<eesti>Maksukohustuslase registreerimisel k&auml;esolevas l&otilde;ikes nimetatud juhtudel v&otilde;etakse aluseks avalduse esmase esitamise kuup&auml;ev. </eesti>
<inglise>In the cases specified in this subsection, the registration of a taxable person shall be based on the date of the first filing of the application. </inglise>
<eesti>(17.11.1999 j&otilde;ust.01.01.2000 - RT I 1999, 92, 823) </eesti>
<inglise>(17.11.1999 entered into force 01.01.2000 - RT I 1999, 92, 823) </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Maksukohustuslase, kes p&auml;rast k&auml;esoleva paragrahvi 1. l&otilde;ikes nimetatud suuruses maksustatava k&auml;ibe tekkimist ei ole esitanud avaldust enda registreerimiseks k&auml;esoleva paragrahvi 1. l&otilde;ikes nimetatud t&auml;htaja jooksul, registreerib Maksuamet maksustatava k&auml;ibe tekkimise kuule j&auml;rgneva kalendrikuu esimesest p&auml;evast. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) A taxable person who, after its taxable supply reached the amount specified in subsection (1) of this section, fails to submit an application for registration of the taxable person during the term specified in subsection (1) of this section shall be registered by the Tax Board as of the first day of the calendar month following the month in which such taxable supply is made. </inglise>
<eesti>Maksuamet registreerib tagasiulatuvalt ka maksukohustuslase, kes ei esitanud t&auml;htaegselt avaldust enda registreerimiseks k&auml;esoleva seaduse kuni 1995. aasta 1. aprillini kehtinud redaktsioonis v&otilde;i Eesti Vabariigi k&auml;ibemaksuseaduses (RT 1991, 36, 447; 1992, 34, 440; RT I 1993, 35, 548; 60, 847) s&auml;testatud suuruses maksustatava k&auml;ibe tekkimisel, kui sellises suuruses maksustatav k&auml;ive tekkis vastava seaduse kehtimise ajal, vastavalt nimetatud suuruses maksustatava k&auml;ibe tekkimise ajal kehtinud korrale. </eesti>
<inglise>A taxable person who failed to submit an application for registration of the taxable person during the prescribed term when its taxable supply reached the amount provided for in the wording of this Act in force until 1 April 1995 or in the Republic of Estonia Value Added Tax Act (RT 1991, 36, 447; 1992, 34, 440; RT I 1993, 35, 548; 60, 847), if the taxable supply in such amount was created during the time the corresponding Act was in force, shall be registered retroactively by the Tax Board pursuant to the procedure in force at the time the taxable supply reached the specified amount. </inglise>
<eesti>(22.02.95 j&otilde;ust.01.04.95 - RT I 1995, 31, 383; 12.06.96 j&otilde;ust.01.09.96 - RT I 1996, 44, 845) </eesti>
<inglise>(22.02.95 entered into force 01.04.95 - RT I 1995, 31, 383; 12.06.96 entered into force 01.09.96 - RT I 1996, 44, 845) </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Maksukohustuslase taotlusel registreerib Maksuamet maksukohustuslase, kelle maksustatav k&auml;ive, v&auml;lja arvatud import, ei &uuml;leta kalendriaastal k&auml;esoleva paragrahvi 1. l&otilde;ikes toodud m&auml;&auml;ra, sealhulgas maksukohustuslase, kellel maksustatavat k&auml;ivet ei ole veel tekkinud, avalduse esitamise kuule j&auml;rgneva kalendrikuu esimesest p&auml;evast. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) On the application of the taxable person, the Tax Board shall register a taxable person whose taxable supply, excluding imports, during a calendar year has not reached the amount specified in subsection (1) of this section, including a taxable person who has not made any taxable supply yet, as of the first day of the calendar month following the month in which the application is submitted. </inglise>
<eesti>Maksukohustuslane esitab enda registreerimiseks Maksuametile rahandusministri poolt kehtestatud vormis avalduse ning k&auml;esoleva paragrahvi 1. ja 1 (1). l&otilde;ikes nimetatud dokumendid. </eesti>
<inglise>In order to be registered as a taxable person, a taxable person shall submit an application in the format established by the Minister of Finance and the documents specified in subsections (1) and (1 (1)) of this section to the Tax Board. </inglise>
<eesti>(12.06.96 j&otilde;ust.01.09.96 - RT I 1996, 44, 845; 17.11.1999 j&otilde;ust.01.01.2000 - RT I 1999, 92, 823) </eesti>
<inglise>(12.06.96 entered into force 01.09.96 - RT I 1996, 44, 845; 17.11.1999 entered into force 01.01.2000 - RT I 1999, 92, 823) </inglise>
<eesti>(4) (Kehtetu - 12.06.96 j&otilde;ust.01.09.96 - RT I 1996, 44, 845) </eesti>
<inglise>(4) (Repealed - 12.06.96 entered into force 01.09.96 - RT I 1996, 44, 845) </inglise>
<eesti>(5) Isik loetakse registreeritud maksukohustuslaseks Maksuameti otsuses t&auml;hendatud p&auml;evast, mil tema suhtes laienevad registreeritud maksukohustuslase &otilde;igused ja kohustused. </eesti>
<inglise>(5) A person is deemed to be a registered taxable person as of the date specified in the decision of the Tax Board, at which time the rights and duties of a registered taxable person extend to the person. </inglise>
<eesti>Oma otsuse teatab Maksuamet maksukohustuslasele kirjalikult 10 p&auml;eva jooksul avalduse saamise p&auml;evast arvates rahandusministri poolt kehtestatud vormis. </eesti>
<inglise>The Tax Board shall notify the taxable person of the decision of the Tax Board in writing and in the format established by the Minister of Finance within ten days after the date of receipt of the application. </inglise>
<eesti>(22.02.95 j&otilde;ust.01.04.95 - RT I 1995, 31, 383; 12.06.96 j&otilde;ust.01.09.96 - RT I 1996, 44, 845) </eesti>
<inglise>(22.02.95 entered into force 01.04.95 - RT I 1995, 31, 383; 12.06.96 entered into force 01.09.96 - RT I 1996, 44, 845) </inglise>
<eesti>(6) Kui Maksuamet tuvastab p&auml;rast maksukohustuslase registreerimist, et maksukohustuslane on esitanud taotluse enda registreerimiseks etten&auml;htust hiljem ning registreeritud maksukohustuslase &otilde;igused ja kohustused oleksid pidanud hakkama tema suhtes kehtima enne Maksuameti otsuses n&auml;idatud kuup&auml;eva, t&uuml;histab Maksuamet oma esialgse otsuse ja registreerib maksukohustuslase uue otsusega tagasiulatuvalt vastavalt k&auml;esoleva paragrahvi 2. l&otilde;ikele. </eesti>
<inglise>(6) If, after registration of a taxable person, the Tax Board ascertains that the taxable person submitted an application for the registration of the taxable person later than prescribed and that the rights and duties of a registered taxable person should have become applicable to the taxable person before the date specified in the decision of the Tax Board, the Tax Board shall repeal its original decision and register the taxable person retroactively by a new decision pursuant to subsection (2) of this section. </inglise>
<eesti>(12.06.96 j&otilde;ust.01.09.96 - RT I 1996, 44, 845) </eesti>
<inglise>(12.06.96 entered into force 01.09.96 - RT I 1996, 44, 845) </inglise>
<eesti>(7) (Kehtetu - 17.11.1999 j&otilde;ust.01.01.2000 - RT I 1999, 92, 823) </eesti>
<inglise>(7) (Repealed - 17.11.1999 entered into force 01.01.2000 - RT I 1999, 92, 823) </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 8. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 8. </inglise>
<eesti>Mitme maksukohustuslase registreerimine &uuml;he maksukohustuslasena </eesti>
<inglise>Registration of several taxable persons as single taxable person </inglise>
<eesti>(12.06.96 j&otilde;ust.01.09.96 - RT I 1996, 44, 845) </eesti>
<inglise>(12.06.96 entered into force 01.09.96 - RT I 1996, 44, 845) </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Maksuamet registreerib rahandusministri poolt kehtestatud korras &uuml;he maksukohustuslasena emaettev&otilde;tja ja t&uuml;tarettev&otilde;tjad &auml;riseadustiku t&auml;henduses, samuti maksukohustuslased, kelle puhul esineb v&auml;hemalt &uuml;ks j&auml;rgmistest asjaoludest: </eesti>
<inglise>(1) A parent undertaking and its subsidiaries as defined in the Commercial Code, and several taxable persons with regard to whom at least one of the following circumstances exists shall be registered by The Tax Board as a single taxable person pursuant to the procedure established by the Minister of Finance: </inglise>
<eesti>1) &uuml;le 50% iga k&auml;esoleva paragrahvi kohaselt registreeritava aktsiaseltsi aktsiatest v&otilde;i osa-, t&auml;is- v&otilde;i usaldus&uuml;hingu osalusest kuulub samale isikule; </eesti>
<inglise>1) more than 50 per cent of the shares of each public limited company to be registered pursuant to this section or of the holdings in each private limited company or a general or limited partnership to be registered pursuant to this section are owned by one and the same person; </inglise>
<eesti>2) &uuml;le 50% iga k&auml;esoleva paragrahvi kohaselt registreeritava aktsiaseltsi aktsiatega, osa&uuml;hingu osadega v&otilde;i t&auml;is- v&otilde;i usaldus&uuml;hingu sissemaksetega m&auml;&auml;ratud h&auml;&auml;ltest kuulub samale isikule. </eesti>
<inglise>2) more than 50 per cent of the votes determined by the shares of each public limited company or private limited company to be registered pursuant to this section or by the contributions into each general or limited partnership to be registered pursuant to this section are owned by one and the same person. </inglise>
<eesti>(17.11.1999 j&otilde;ust.01.01.2000 - RT I 1999, 92, 823) </eesti>
<inglise>(17.11.1999 entered into force 01.01.2000 - RT I 1999, 92, 823) </inglise>
<eesti>(2) K&auml;ibemaksukohustuslasena registreerimata maksukohustuslased registreeritakse enne nende &uuml;he maksukohustuslasena registreerimist eraldi maksukohustuslastena k&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect;-s 7 s&auml;testatud korras. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) Before taxable persons who have not been registered as persons liable to value added tax are registered as a single taxable person, they shall be registered as separate taxable persons pursuant to the procedure provided for in &sect; 7 of this Act. </inglise>
<eesti>(17.11.1999 j&otilde;ust.01.01.2000 - RT I 1999, 92, 823) </eesti>
<inglise>(17.11.1999 entered into force 01.01.2000 - RT I 1999, 92, 823) </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Maksuamet tunnistab &uuml;he maksukohustuslasena registreerimise otsuse kehtetuks, kui &uuml;he maksukohustuslasena registreeritud maksukohustuslaste puhul ei esine enam &uuml;htki k&auml;esoleva paragrahvi 1. l&otilde;ikes nimetatud asjaoludest, nende asjaolude l&otilde;ppemise kuule j&auml;rgneva kalendrikuu esimesest p&auml;evast. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) If none of the circumstances specified in subsection (1) of this section any longer exists with regard to taxable persons registered as a single taxable person, the Tax Board shall annul the decision concerning registration as a single taxable person as of the first day of the calendar month following the month in which the circumstances ceased to exist. </inglise>
<eesti>&Uuml;he maksukohustuslasena registreeritud maksukohustuslaste taotlusel tunnistab Maksuamet &uuml;he maksukohustuslasena registreerimise otsuse kehtetuks rahandusministri kehtestatud tingimustel ja korras. </eesti>
<inglise>At the request of taxable persons registered as a single taxable person, the Tax Board shall annul the decision concerning registration as a single taxable person under the conditions and pursuant to the procedure established by the Minister of Finance. </inglise>
<eesti>(17.11.1999 j&otilde;ust.01.01.2000 - RT I 1999, 92, 823) </eesti>
<inglise>(17.11.1999 entered into force 01.01.2000 - RT I 1999, 92, 823) </inglise>
<eesti>(4) &Uuml;he maksukohustuslasena registreerimise otsuse kehtetuks tunnistamise p&auml;evast loetakse maksukohustuslased uuesti registreerituteks eraldi maksukohustuslastena. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) As of the date of the annulment of a decision concerning registration as a single taxable person, the taxable persons are deemed to be re-registered as separate taxable persons. </inglise>
<eesti>(17.11.1999 j&otilde;ust.01.01.2000 - RT I 1999, 92, 823) </eesti>
<inglise>(17.11.1999 entered into force 01.01.2000 - RT I 1999, 92, 823) </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 9. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 9. </inglise>
<eesti>Maksuameti kohustus maksukohustuslase registreerimisel </eesti>
<inglise>Duty of Tax Board upon registration of taxable persons </inglise>
<eesti>Maksuamet on kohustatud registreerimisel selgitama maksukohustuslasele tema kohustusi k&auml;ibemaksu maksmisel. </eesti>
<inglise>Upon registering a taxable person, the Tax Board is required to explain the duties of the taxable person upon payment of value added tax to the taxable person. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 10. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 10. </inglise>
<eesti>Registreeritud maksukohustuslase kohustused </eesti>
<inglise>Duties of registered taxable persons </inglise>
<eesti>Registreeritud maksukohustuslane on kohustatud: </eesti>
<inglise>Registered taxable persons are required: </inglise>
<eesti>1) arvestama enda ettev&otilde;tluse tulemusena tekkivalt maksustatavalt k&auml;ibelt k&auml;ibemaksu k&auml;esoleva seaduse paragrahvis 13 nimetatud m&auml;&auml;ra j&auml;rgi; </eesti>
<inglise>1) to calculate value added tax on taxable supply made as a result of their engagement in enterprise according to the rates specified in &sect; 13 of this Act; </inglise>
<eesti>2) arvutama k&auml;esoleva seaduse paragrahvis 18 s&auml;testatud korras tasumisele kuuluva k&auml;ibemaksu summa; </eesti>
<inglise>2) to calculate the amount of value added tax due pursuant to the procedure provided for in &sect; 18 of this Act; </inglise>
<eesti>3) esitama Maksuametile rahandusministri poolt kehtestatud vormis k&auml;ibedeklaratsiooni; </eesti>
<inglise>3) to submit a value added tax return in the format established by the Minister of Finance to the Tax Board; </inglise>
<eesti>4) tasuma enda ettev&otilde;tluse tulemusena tekkivalt maksustatavalt k&auml;ibelt, v&auml;lja arvatud impordilt, ning teiselt registreeritud maksukohustuslaselt ostetud kasvava metsa raie&otilde;iguse, metsamaterjali, saematerjali v&otilde;i nende materjalide transpordi- ja valmistamisteenuste maksustatavalt k&auml;ibelt k&auml;ibemaksu k&auml;ibedeklaratsiooni esitamise t&auml;htp&auml;evaks ning impordilt tollieeskirjades s&auml;testatud impordimaksude (tolliseaduse m&otilde;istes) tasumise t&auml;htp&auml;evaks. </eesti>
<inglise>4) to pay value added tax on taxable supply made as a result of their engagement in enterprise, excluding imports, and on taxable supply of rights to cut standing crop, of timber, sawn timber or the transport and manufacturing services of the timber purchased from another registered taxable person, by the due date for submission of the value added tax return, and to pay value added tax on imports by the due date for payment of import charges (as defined in the Customs Act) provided for in the customs rules. </inglise>
<eesti>Eesti kaupade nomenklatuuri rubriigid ja alamrubriigid, millesse kuuluvaid tooteid k&auml;sitatakse k&auml;esoleva seaduse t&auml;henduses metsa- v&otilde;i saematerjalina, m&auml;&auml;rab rahandusminister; </eesti>
<inglise>The Minister of Finance shall determine the headings and subheadings of the Nomenclature of Estonian Commodities under which the goods are deemed to be timber or sawn timber within the meaning of this Act; </inglise>
<eesti>(17.11.1999 j&otilde;ust.01.01.2000 - RT I 1999, 92, 823; 06.03.2001 j&otilde;ust.01.04.2001 - RT I 2001, 26, 148) </eesti>
<inglise>(17.11.1999 entered into force 01.01.2000 - RT I 1999, 92, 823; 06.03.2001 entered into force 01.04.2001 - RT I 2001, 26, 148) </inglise>
<eesti>5) v&auml;ljastama ning s&auml;ilitama arveid k&auml;esoleva seaduse paragrahvides 24 ja 25 s&auml;testatud tingimustel ja korras. </eesti>
<inglise>5) to issue and preserve invoices under the conditions and pursuant to the procedures provided for in &sect;&sect; 24 and 25 of this Act. </inglise>
<eesti>(22.02.95 j&otilde;ust.01.04.95 - RT I 1995, 31, 383; 12.06.96 j&otilde;ust.01.09.96 - RT I 1996, 44, 845) </eesti>
<inglise>(22.02.95 entered into force 01.04.95 - RT I 1995, 31, 383; 12.06.96 entered into force 01.09.96 - RT I 1996, 44, 845) </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 11. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 11. </inglise>
<eesti>Maksukohustuslase registrist kustutamine </eesti>
<inglise>Deletion of taxable person from register </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Isik, kes on olnud Maksuametis registreeritud v&auml;hemalt kaks aastat, kuid kelle maksustatav k&auml;ive viimasel kalendriaastal, v&auml;lja arvatud import, ei &uuml;letanud ega &uuml;leta tema arvestuste kohaselt ka jooksval kalendriaastal k&auml;esoleva seaduse paragrahvi 7 1. l&otilde;ikes toodud m&auml;&auml;ra, v&otilde;ib esitada Maksuametile avalduse enda registrist kustutamiseks. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) A person who has been registered with the Tax Board for at least two years but whose taxable supply, excluding imports, in the previous calendar year did not exceed and, according to the calculations of the taxable person, in the current calendar year will not exceed the amount specified in subsection 7 (1) of this Act may submit an application to the Tax Board for deletion of the taxable person from the register. </inglise>
<eesti>Maksuamet v&otilde;ib maksukohustuslase registrist kustutada p&auml;rast tema majandustegevuse kontrollimist. </eesti>
<inglise>The Tax Board may delete a taxable person from the register after auditing the economic activities of the taxable person. </inglise>
<eesti>(22.02.95 j&otilde;ust.01.04.95 - RT I 1995, 31, 383) </eesti>
<inglise>(22.02.95 entered into force 01.04.95 - RT I 1995, 31, 383) </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Maksuametil on &otilde;igus kustutada registrist isik, kelle poolt maksustamisperioodi maksustatavalt k&auml;ibelt arvutatud k&auml;ibemaks on v&auml;hemalt kolme &uuml;ksteisele j&auml;rgneva maksustamisperioodi jooksul olnud v&auml;iksem tema poolt kaupade ja teenuste soetamisel makstud k&auml;ibemaksu summast, kui see ei ole tingitud k&auml;ibemaksu m&auml;&auml;raga 0% maksustatavast k&auml;ibest. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The Tax Board has the right to delete a person from the register if the value added tax calculated by the person on taxable supply during a taxable period has, during at least three consecutive taxable periods, been less than the amount of value added tax paid by the person upon purchasing goods or services, unless this is due to supply subject to the value added tax rate of 0 per cent. </inglise>
<eesti>(22.02.95 j&otilde;ust.01.04.95 - RT I 1995, 31, 383; 12.06.96 j&otilde;ust.01.09.96 - RT I 1996, 44, 845) </eesti>
<inglise>(22.02.95 entered into force 01.04.95 - RT I 1995, 31, 383; 12.06.96 entered into force 01.09.96 - RT I 1996, 44, 845) </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Maksuametil on &otilde;igus kustutada registrist maksukohustuslane, kes ei ole esitanud k&auml;ibedeklaratsiooni kuue j&auml;rjestikuse maksustamisperioodi kohta ja tema viimase maksustamisperioodi k&auml;ibedeklaratsiooni esitamise t&auml;htaeg on m&ouml;&ouml;dunud. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) The Tax Board has the right to delete a taxable person from the register if the taxable person has failed to submit a value added tax return for six consecutive taxable periods and the term for submission of the value added tax return for the last taxable period has expired. </inglise>
<eesti>(12.06.96 j&otilde;ust.01.09.96 - RT I 1996, 44, 845) </eesti>
<inglise>(12.06.96 entered into force 01.09.96 - RT I 1996, 44, 845) </inglise>
<eesti>(4) Isik loetakse registrist kustutatuks alates Maksuameti otsuses n&auml;idatud kuup&auml;evast. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) A person is deemed to be deleted from the register as of the date specified in the decision of the Tax Board. </inglise>
<eesti>(12.06.96 j&otilde;ust.01.09.96 - RT I 1996, 44, 845) </eesti>
<inglise>(12.06.96 entered into force 01.09.96 - RT I 1996, 44, 845) </inglise>
<eesti>III peat&uuml;kk </eesti>
<inglise>Chapter III </inglise>
<eesti>Maksustamise &uuml;ldp&otilde;him&otilde;tted </eesti>
<inglise>General Principles of Taxation </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 12. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 12. </inglise>
<eesti>Maksustatav v&auml;&auml;rtus </eesti>
<inglise>Taxable value </inglise>
<eesti>(1) V&auml;lja arvatud k&auml;esoleva paragrahvi 2.-9. l&otilde;ikes s&auml;testatud juhtudel, on maksustatava k&auml;ibe maksustatavaks v&auml;&auml;rtuseks kaupade v&otilde;i teenuste m&uuml;&uuml;gihind, millele on lisatud k&otilde;ik muud kaupade v&otilde;i teenuste saaja poolt kaupade v&otilde;i teenuste m&uuml;&uuml;jale maksmisele kuuluvad summad, v&auml;lja arvatud k&auml;esoleva seadusega kehtestatud maks. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) Except in the cases provided for in subsections (2) -(9) of this section, the taxable value of taxable supply is the selling price of goods or services to which all other amounts to be paid by the recipient of the goods or services to the seller of the goods or services, excluding the tax established by this Act, are added. </inglise>
<eesti>(12.06.96 j&otilde;ust.01.09.96 - RT I 1996, 44, 845) </eesti>
<inglise>(12.06.96 entered into force 01.09.96 - RT I 1996, 44, 845) </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Kapitalirendil on maksustatavaks v&auml;&auml;rtuseks maksustamisperioodil kapitalirendile andjale kapitalirendi makse osana tasutav vara v&auml;ljaostumakse koos intressiga. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) For the purposes of a financial lease, the taxable value is the down payment for the asset, including interest, to be paid to the financial lessor as part of the financial lease payment during a taxable period. </inglise>
<eesti>(12.06.96 j&otilde;ust.01.09.96 - RT I 1996, 44, 845) </eesti>
<inglise>(12.06.96 entered into force 01.09.96 - RT I 1996, 44, 845) </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Kasutusrendil on maksustatavaks v&auml;&auml;rtuseks maksustamisperioodil lepingu j&auml;rgi tasumisele kuuluv summa. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) For the purposes of an operating lease, the taxable value is the amount due during a taxable period pursuant to the contract. </inglise>
<eesti>(12.06.96 j&otilde;ust.01.09.96 - RT I 1996, 44, 845) </eesti>
<inglise>(12.06.96 entered into force 01.09.96 - RT I 1996, 44, 845) </inglise>
<eesti>(4) J&auml;relmaksuga m&uuml;&uuml;gil on maksustatavaks v&auml;&auml;rtuseks j&auml;relmaksuga m&uuml;&uuml;dava kauba m&uuml;&uuml;gihind, v&auml;lja arvatud intress. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) For the purposes of a hire purchase, the taxable value is the selling price, excluding interest, of the goods sold on hire purchase. </inglise>
<eesti>(12.06.96 j&otilde;ust.01.09.96 - RT I 1996, 44, 845) </eesti>
<inglise>(12.06.96 entered into force 01.09.96 - RT I 1996, 44, 845) </inglise>
<eesti>(5) Teenuse osutamisel, mis seisneb teistele isikutele kuuluvate kaupade, teenuste, kinnisasjade, ehitiste kui vallasasjade, raha ja v&auml;&auml;rtpaberite m&uuml;&uuml;gi vahendamises, on rahandusministri poolt kehtestatud tingimustel ja korras maksustatavaks v&auml;&auml;rtuseks vahendustasu. </eesti>
