<eesti>&sect; 22. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 22. </inglise>
<eesti>Kasutatud kaupade m&uuml;&uuml;k ja oksjonim&uuml;&uuml;k </eesti>
<inglise>Sale and sale by auction of used goods </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Kasutatud kaupade m&uuml;&uuml;misel komisjonim&uuml;&uuml;gi vormis maksab komisjon&auml;r k&auml;ibemaksu komisjonitasult. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) If used goods are sold by commission sale, the broker shall pay value added tax on the commission. </inglise>
<eesti>(22.02.95 j&otilde;ust.01.04.95 - RT I 1995, 31, 383) </eesti>
<inglise>(22.02.95 entered into force 01.04.95 - RT I 1995, 31, 383) </inglise>
<eesti>(1 (1)) Maksukohustuslasena registreerimata isikult Eestis ostetud kasutatud kauba ja kultuuriv&auml;&auml;rtusega asjade edasim&uuml;&uuml;misel maksab edasim&uuml;&uuml;ja k&auml;ibemaksu edasim&uuml;&uuml;dud kauba ja kultuuriv&auml;&auml;rtusega asjade k&auml;ibemaksuta m&uuml;&uuml;gihinna ja ostuhinna vahelt. </eesti>
<inglise>(1 (1)) If used goods and things of cultural value are bought in Estonia from a person not registered as a taxable person and resold, the reseller shall pay value added tax on the difference between the selling price net of VAT and the purchase price of the resold goods and things of cultural value. </inglise>
<eesti>K&auml;ibemaksuga maksustamisel v&otilde;etakse arvesse ainult edasim&uuml;&uuml;gi positiivne hinnavahe. </eesti>
<inglise>Only positive price difference upon resale is taken into account in the imposition of value added tax. </inglise>
<eesti>(14.11.2000 j&otilde;ust.01.01.2000 - RT I 2000, 89, 581) </eesti>
<inglise>(14.11.2000 entered into force 01.01.2000 - RT I 2000, 89, 581) </inglise>
<eesti>(2) K&auml;esoleva paragrahvi 1. ja 1 (1). l&otilde;ikes s&auml;testatut rakendatakse vaid juhul, kui neis nimetatud kaupu ei m&uuml;&uuml;da partiidena ja neid m&uuml;&uuml;akse uutest kaupadest eraldi. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The provisions of subsections (1) and (1 (1)) of this section apply only if goods specified therein are not sold in lots and they are sold separately from new goods. </inglise>
<eesti>(14.11.2000 j&otilde;ust.01.01.2000 - RT I 2000, 89, 581) </eesti>
<inglise>(14.11.2000 entered into force 01.01.2000 - RT I 2000, 89, 581) </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Oksjonim&uuml;&uuml;gi k&auml;ibelt maksab oksjoni korraldaja k&auml;ibemaksu kaupade vahendamise eest saadavalt tasult. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) The organiser of an auction shall pay value added tax on the supply of a sale by auction from the fee received for intermediating the goods. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 23. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 23. </inglise>
<eesti>Enne registreerimist soetatud kaupadelt makstud k&auml;ibemaksu mahaarvamine </eesti>
<inglise>Deduction of value added tax paid on goods purchased before registration </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Registreeritud maksukohustuslasel, kellel on laos enne tema registreeritud maksukohustuslase &otilde;iguste ja kohustuste tekkimise p&auml;eva soetatud kaupu, millelt on makstud k&auml;ibemaksu, on Maksuameti loal &otilde;igus oma maksustatavalt k&auml;ibelt arvestatud k&auml;ibemaksust maha arvata nendelt kaupadelt tasutud k&auml;ibemaksusummad k&auml;esoleva seaduse paragrahvi 24 1.l&otilde;ikes s&auml;testatud n&otilde;uetele vastava arve v&otilde;i impordi kaubadeklaratsiooni alusel. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) If a registered taxable person has inventory which was purchased before the date on which the rights and duties of a registered taxable person arose with regard to the taxable person, and if the registered taxable person has paid value added tax on such goods, the registered taxable person has the right, with the permission of the Tax Board, to deduct the amounts of value added tax paid on such goods from the value added tax calculated on the taxable supply of the registered taxable person, on the basis of an invoice which complies with the requirements provided for in subsection 24 (1) of this Act or on the basis of a declaration of goods for import. </inglise>
<eesti>(22.02.95 j&otilde;ust.01.04.95 - RT I 1995, 31, 383) </eesti>
<inglise>(22.02.95 entered into force 01.04.95 - RT I 1995, 31, 383) </inglise>
<eesti>(2) K&auml;esoleva paragrahvi 1. l&otilde;ikes nimetatud summade mahaarvamine toimub Maksuameti poolt m&auml;&auml;ratud perioodi jooksul ning korras. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The amounts specified in subsection (1) of this section shall be deducted during the period and pursuant to the procedure provided by the Tax Board. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 24. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 24. </inglise>
<eesti>Arved </eesti>
<inglise>Invoices </inglise>
<eesti>(1) V&auml;lja arvatud rahandusministri m&auml;&auml;ratud juhtudel vastavalt k&auml;esoleva paragrahvi 2. l&otilde;ikes s&auml;testatule, on registreeritud maksukohustuslane kohustatud kauba v&otilde;i teenuse v&otilde;&otilde;randamisel esitama ostjale k&auml;esoleva paragrahvi 7. l&otilde;ikes nimetatud t&auml;htaja jooksul arve, millele on m&auml;rgitud: </eesti>
<inglise>(1) Except in the cases specified by the Minister of Finance pursuant to the provisions of subsection (2) of this section, a registered taxable person is required, upon the transfer of goods or services, to submit an invoice to the purchaser during the term specified in subsection (7) of this section, which shall set out: </inglise>
<eesti>1) m&uuml;&uuml;ja nimi, aadress ja registreerimisnumber v&otilde;i isikukood ning k&auml;ibemaksukohustuslasena registreerimise number; </eesti>
<inglise>1) the name, address, registration number or personal identification code and the number of registration as a person liable to value added tax of the seller; </inglise>
<eesti>(17.11.1999 j&otilde;ust.01.01.2000 - RT I 1999, 92, 823) </eesti>
<inglise>(17.11.1999 entered into force 01.01.2000 - RT I 1999, 92, 823) </inglise>
<eesti>2) arve number ja v&auml;ljastamise kuup&auml;ev; </eesti>
<inglise>2) the number and date of issue of the invoice; </inglise>
<eesti>3) ostja nimi ning aadress; </eesti>
<inglise>3) the name and address of the purchaser; </inglise>
<eesti>4) kauba v&otilde;i teenuse nimetus, kogus, hind kroonides ning kaupade ja teenuste kogumaksumus ilma k&auml;ibemaksuta ja koos k&auml;ibemaksuga k&auml;ibemaksu m&auml;&auml;rade l&otilde;ikes; </eesti>
<inglise>4) the name, quantity, and price in kroons of the goods or services, and the total cost of the goods or services with and without value added tax separately by different rates of value added tax; </inglise>
<eesti>(17.11.1999 j&otilde;ust.01.01.2000 - RT I 1999, 92, 823) </eesti>
<inglise>(17.11.1999 entered into force 01.01.2000 - RT I 1999, 92, 823) </inglise>
<eesti>5) kauba v&otilde;i teenuse maksustatav v&auml;&auml;rtus, juhul kui see on erinev k&auml;esoleva l&otilde;ike punktis 4 nimetatud hinnast; </eesti>
<inglise>5) the taxable value of the goods or services if different from the price specified in clause 4) of this section; </inglise>
<eesti>6) k&auml;ibemaksusumma k&auml;ibemaksu m&auml;&auml;rade l&otilde;ikes; </eesti>
<inglise>6) the amounts of value added tax separately by different tax rates; </inglise>
<eesti>(17.11.1999 j&otilde;ust.01.01.2000 - RT I 1999, 92, 823) </eesti>
<inglise>(17.11.1999 entered into force 01.01.2000 - RT I 1999, 92, 823) </inglise>
<eesti>7) kauba v&auml;ljastamise v&otilde;i teenuse osutamise kuup&auml;ev, juhul kui see on erinev arve v&auml;ljastamise kuup&auml;evast; </eesti>
<inglise>7) the date of delivery of the goods or provision of the services if different from the date of issue of the invoice; </inglise>
<eesti>8) (Kehtetu - 17.11.1999 j&otilde;ust.01.01.2000 - RT I 1999, 92, 823) </eesti>
<inglise>8) (Repealed - 17.11.1999 entered into force 01.01.2000 - RT I 1999, 92, 823) </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Rahandusministril on &otilde;igus m&auml;&auml;rata juhtumid, mil registreeritud maksukohustuslase poolt arve esitamine ostjale ei ole kohustuslik. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The Minister of Finance has the right to specify cases in which registered taxable persons are not required to submit invoices to purchasers. </inglise>
<eesti>Ostja taotlusel on registreeritud maksukohustuslane alati kohustatud v&auml;ljastama talle k&auml;esoleva paragrahvi 1. l&otilde;ikes s&auml;testatud n&otilde;uetele vastava arve. </eesti>
<inglise>On the application of a purchaser, a registered taxable person is always required to issue an invoice which complies with the requirements provided for in subsection (1) of this section to the purchaser. </inglise>
<eesti>(22.02.95 j&otilde;ust.01.04.95 - RT I 1995, 31, 383; 24.10.96 j&otilde;ust.06.11.96 - RT I 1996, 76, 1344) </eesti>
<inglise>(22.02.95 entered into force 01.04.95 - RT I 1995, 31, 383; 24.10.96 entered into force 06.11.96 - RT I 1996, 76, 1344) </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Regulaarselt osutatavate teenuste ja &uuml;leantavate kaupade puhul on registreeritud maksukohustuslasel &otilde;igus v&auml;ljastada ostjale k&auml;esoleva paragrahvi 1. l&otilde;ikes s&auml;testatud n&otilde;uetele vastav arve &uuml;ks kord kuus. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) In the case of the regular provision of services or transfer of goods, a registered taxable person has the right to issue an invoice which complies with the requirements provided for in subsection (1) of this section to the purchaser once a month. </inglise>
<eesti>F&uuml;&uuml;silisest isikust regulaarsele ostjale, kes ei tegutse ettev&otilde;tjana, on registreeritud maksukohustuslasel juhul, kui tema poolt sellele ostjale kalendrikuu jooksul v&otilde;&otilde;randatavate kaupade ja teenuste kogumaksumus koos k&auml;ibemaksuga ei &uuml;leta 250 krooni, &otilde;igus v&auml;ljastada k&auml;esoleva paragrahvi 1. l&otilde;ikes s&auml;testatud n&otilde;uetele vastav arve &uuml;ks kord kuni kuuekuulise perioodi eest. </eesti>
<inglise>If the total cost together with value tax of the goods and services which a registered taxable person transfers during a calendar month to a regular purchaser who is a natural person and does not engage in enterprise does not exceed 250 kroons, the taxable person has the right to issue an invoice in compliance with the requirements provided for in subsection (1) of this section to such purchaser once for a period of up to six months. </inglise>
<eesti>(17.11.1999 j&otilde;ust.01.01.2000 - RT I 1999, 92, 823) </eesti>
<inglise>(17.11.1999 entered into force 01.01.2000 - RT I 1999, 92, 823) </inglise>
<eesti>(4) Arvel v&otilde;i muul dokumendil ei tohi n&auml;idata k&auml;ibemaksu summat isik, kes ei ole registreeritud maksukohustuslane. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) A person who is not a registered taxable person shall not indicate the amount of value added tax on an invoice or other document. </inglise>
<eesti>(22.02.95 j&otilde;ust.01.04.95 - RT I 1995, 31, 383) </eesti>
<inglise>(22.02.95 entered into force 01.04.95 - RT I 1995, 31, 383) </inglise>
<eesti>(5) Registreeritud maksukohustuslane ei tohi kauba v&otilde;i teenuse ostjale esitatavas arves n&auml;idata k&auml;ibemaksu summat: </eesti>
<inglise>(5) A registered taxable person shall not indicate, on an invoice submitted to a purchaser of goods or services, value added tax: </inglise>
<eesti>1) kaupade ja teenuste kohta, mille k&auml;ivet k&auml;esoleva seaduse paragrahv 5 kohaselt ei maksustata; </eesti>
<inglise>1) on goods or services the supply of which is exempt from tax pursuant to &sect; 5 of this Act; </inglise>
<eesti>2) tehingute kohta, mis k&auml;esoleva seaduse kohaselt ei ole k&auml;ibemaksu objektiks; </eesti>
<inglise>2) on transactions which pursuant to this Act are not objects of value added tax; </inglise>
<eesti>3) m&uuml;&uuml;giobjektide kohta, mis k&auml;esoleva seaduse m&otilde;istes ei ole kaubad ega teenused; </eesti>
<inglise>3) on objects of sale which are not goods or services as defined in this Act; </inglise>
<eesti>4) kauba v&otilde;i teenuse kohta, mille puhul k&auml;ibemaksum&auml;&auml;r on 0%. </eesti>
<inglise>4) on goods or services subject to a value added tax rate of 0 per cent. </inglise>
<eesti>(22.02.95 j&otilde;ust.01.04.95 - RT I 1995, 31, 383) </eesti>
<inglise>(22.02.95 entered into force 01.04.95 - RT I 1995, 31, 383) </inglise>
<eesti>(6) Kui arve v&otilde;i muu dokument, millel on n&auml;idatud k&auml;ibemaksu summa, on v&auml;ljastatud k&auml;esoleva paragrahvi 4. ja 5. l&otilde;ikes s&auml;testatud tingimuste vastaselt, on dokumendi v&auml;ljastanud isik kohustatud sellele j&auml;rgneva kuu 20. kuup&auml;evaks maksma riigieelarvesse tema poolt v&auml;ljastatud arvel v&otilde;i muul m&uuml;&uuml;gidokumendil n&auml;idatud k&auml;ibemaksu summa, olenemata sellest, kas see muul juhul oleks kuulunud maksmisele. </eesti>
<inglise>(6) If an invoice or other document on which an amount of value added tax is indicated is issued in violation of the requirements provided for in subsection (4) or (5) of this section, the person who issues the document is required to pay the amount of value added tax indicated on the invoice or other document issued by the person concerning the sale of goods or services into the state budget by the twentieth day of the following month, regardless of whether the amount is otherwise payable. </inglise>
<eesti>Kui arvel v&otilde;i muul m&uuml;&uuml;gidokumendil n&auml;idatud k&auml;ibemaksusumma on arvestatud vastavate kaupade v&otilde;i teenuste k&auml;ibele k&auml;esoleva seadusega kehtestatud k&auml;ibemaksu m&auml;&auml;rast k&otilde;rgema m&auml;&auml;ra j&auml;rgi, on dokumendi v&auml;ljastanud isik kohustatud j&auml;rgmise kuu 20. kuup&auml;evaks maksma riigieelarvesse tema poolt v&auml;ljastatud arvel v&otilde;i muul m&uuml;&uuml;gidokumendil n&auml;idatud k&auml;ibemaksu summa, olenemata sellest, kas see muul juhul oleks kuulunud maksmisele. </eesti>
<inglise>If the amount of value added tax indicated on an invoice or other document concerning the sale of goods or services is calculated according to a rate higher than the rate of value added tax established by this Act for the supply of the corresponding goods or services, the person who issues the document is required to pay the amount of value added tax indicated on the invoice or other document issued by the person concerning the sale of goods or services into the state budget by the twentieth day of the following month, regardless of whether the amount is otherwise payable. </inglise>
<eesti>(22.02.95 j&otilde;ust.01.04.95 - RT I 1995, 31, 383; 17.11.1999 j&otilde;ust.01.01.2000 - RT I 1999, 92, 823) </eesti>
<inglise>(22.02.95 entered into force 01.04.95 - RT I 1995, 31, 383; 17.11.1999 entered into force 01.01.2000 - RT I 1999, 92, 823) </inglise>
<eesti>(7) Registreeritud maksukohustuslane on kohustatud esitama ostjale arve seitsme kalendrip&auml;eva jooksul, arvates kauba l&auml;hetamise v&otilde;i ostjale k&auml;ttesaadavaks tegemise v&otilde;i teenuse osutamise p&auml;evast. </eesti>
<inglise>(7) A registered taxable person is required to submit an invoice to a purchaser within seven calendar days after the date on which goods are dispatched or made available to the purchaser or on which services are provided. </inglise>
<eesti>Juhul kui maksukohustuslasel on &otilde;igus vastavalt k&auml;esoleva paragrahvi 3. l&otilde;ikele esitada ostjale arve &uuml;ks kord kuus, on ta kohustatud esitama arve hiljemalt kauba l&auml;hetamise v&otilde;i ostjale k&auml;ttesaadavaks tegemise v&otilde;i teenuse osutamise kuule j&auml;rgneva kuu 7. p&auml;eval. </eesti>
<inglise>If, pursuant to subsection (3) of this section, a taxable person has the right to submit an invoice to a purchaser once a month, the taxable person is required to submit the invoice not later than on the seventh day of the month following the month during which the goods are dispatched or made available to the purchaser or during which the services are provided. </inglise>
<eesti>Kui maksukohustuslasel on vastavalt samale l&otilde;ikele &otilde;igus esitada f&uuml;&uuml;silisest isikust ostjale arve &uuml;ks kord kuni kuuekuulise perioodi eest, on ta kohustatud esitama arve hiljemalt kauba l&auml;hetamise v&otilde;i ostjale k&auml;ttesaadavaks tegemise v&otilde;i teenuse osutamise perioodile, mille eest arve esitatakse, j&auml;rgneva kuu 7. p&auml;eval. </eesti>
<inglise>If, pursuant to the same subsection, a taxable person has the right to submit an invoice to a purchaser who is a natural person once for a period of up to six months, the taxable person is required to submit the invoice not later than on the seventh day of the month following the period during which the goods are dispatched or made available to the purchaser or the services are provided and for which the invoice is submitted. </inglise>
<eesti>(12.06.96 j&otilde;ust.01.09.96 - RT I 1996, 44, 845; 17.11.1999 j&otilde;ust.01.01.2000 - RT I 1999, 92, 823) </eesti>
<inglise>(12.06.96 entered into force 01.09.96 - RT I 1996, 44, 845; 17.11.1999 entered into force 01.01.2000 - RT I 1999, 92, 823) </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 25. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 25. </inglise>
<eesti>Arvete s&auml;ilitamine ning arvepidamise kord </eesti>
<inglise>Procedure for preservation of invoices and maintenance of records </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Registreeritud maksukohustuslane on kohustatud s&auml;ilitama kronoloogilises j&auml;rjekorras k&otilde;igi enda v&auml;ljastatud arvete koopiad, k&otilde;ik saadud kaupade v&otilde;i teenuste soetamisel k&auml;ibemaksu tasumist t&otilde;endavad arved ning impordilt k&auml;ibemaksu tasumist t&otilde;endavad kaubadeklaratsioonid seitsme aasta jooksul, arvates nende v&auml;ljastamise v&otilde;i saamise p&auml;evast. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) A registered taxable person is required to preserve copies of all invoices issued by the taxable person, all invoices received certifying payment of value added tax upon the purchase of goods or services, and declarations of goods for import certifying payment of value added tax on imports, in chronological order for seven years after the date of issue or receipt of the invoices. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Rahandusminister kehtestab registreeritud maksukohustuslastele igap&auml;evase ning igakuise arvepidamise korra. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The procedure for the daily and monthly maintenance of records by registered taxable persons shall be established by the Minister of Finance. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 26. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 26. </inglise>
<eesti>Tegevuse l&otilde;petamine </eesti>
<inglise>Termination of activities </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Registreeritud maksukohustuslase tegevuse l&otilde;petamisel ning &auml;ri&uuml;hingu &uuml;hinemisel, jagunemisel v&otilde;i &uuml;mberkujundamisel, samuti pankrotimenetluse k&auml;igus v&otilde;&otilde;randatavate kaupade ja teenuste k&auml;ive maksustatakse k&auml;ibemaksuga, v&auml;lja arvatud k&auml;esoleva seaduse paragrahv 3 4. l&otilde;ike punktides 4 ja 7 s&auml;testatud juhtudel. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) The supply of goods and services transferred upon termination of the activities of a registered taxable person, upon the merger, division or transformation of a company, or in the course of bankruptcy proceedings shall be subject to value added tax, except in the cases provided for in clauses 3 (4) 4) and 7) of this Act. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Kui registreeritud maksukohustuslaseks olev f&uuml;&uuml;silisest isikust ettev&otilde;tja on oma tegevuse likvideerimisel v&otilde;&otilde;randanud kogu oma vara, peab ta esitama Maksuametile k&auml;ibedeklaratsiooni ja tasuma etten&auml;htud k&auml;ibemaksu. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) If a registered taxable person who is a sole proprietor has transferred all the assets of the taxable person upon liquidation of the activities of the taxable person, the taxable person shall submit a value added tax return to the Tax Board and shall pay the prescribed value added tax. </inglise>
<eesti>P&auml;rast maksukohustuste t&auml;itmist kustutab Maksuamet maksukohustuslase registrist. </eesti>
<inglise>After fulfilment of the obligation to pay taxes which are due, the Tax Board shall delete the taxable person from the register. </inglise>
